Palaeoenvironment. Coastal, inner neritic. The assemblage from Steinebrunn suggests shallow sublittoral environments with sea grass ( Harzhauser & Landau 2019 ).At the Niederleis section, sediment and fossils from coastal and lagoonal environments not exceeding 30 m water depth were transported by tempestites into offshore settings (
Mandic et al . 2002
).

